{"tid":1146699,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【識英雄重英雄】《鐵達尼號》導演占士金馬倫撰文 致敬《復仇者聯盟4》","createTime":"2019-05-09T11:45:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T15:44:06.000Z","uid":66923,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bf9d62ac017f54210a089e33a30f7feddc6da896","tid":1146699,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T11:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PrRyqHL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPrRyqHL.jpg&h=ffc18674&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n失去賣座亞軍位置的《鐵達尼號》導演占士金馬倫向《復仇者聯盟4》致意<br />\n<br />\nMarvel重頭戲《復仇者聯盟4：終局之戰》票房報捷，截至前日為止，全球累積票房收逾22.7億美元（約177.2億港元），早已超越金像導演占士金馬倫（James Cameron）的經典愛情片《鐵達尼號》（21.87億美元），榮登史上最賣座電影第2位。<br />\n<br />\n雖然占士金馬倫曾批評這類超級英雄片劇情無聊，欠缺科學常識，但他仍尊重傳統，今日透過社交媒體撰文，向《復仇者聯盟4》致敬：「奇雲費格（Marvel電影公司總裁）和Marvel所有人，當年鐵達尼號撞向冰塊而沉沒，如今我的《鐵達尼號》被《復仇者聯盟4》擊沉。本公司向你們致敬，你們證明了電影產業不僅存活，甚至更比任何時候更要強大。」"},{"pid":"dcf68eec9a715bda0192379b9f06da9869118fba","tid":1146699,"uid":48942,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T12:09:03.000Z","msg":"好快超越埋阿凡達啦"},{"pid":"343d2e70acbf98bb0d448c5da99bd2293befa33a","tid":1146699,"uid":149494,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T12:40:45.000Z","msg":"Avatar系列而家屬於disney嘅<br />\n叫你james cameron幫russo brothers奶屎眼都要照做啦"},{"pid":"636410a2104fe9ef0d42c8a32b4d7898a7d11348","tid":1146699,"uid":159798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"343d2e70acbf98bb0d448c5da99bd2293befa33a","tid":1146699,"uid":149494,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T12:40:45.000Z","msg":"Avatar系列而家屬於disney嘅<br />\n叫你james cameron幫russo brothers奶屎眼都要照做啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T12:50:01.000Z","msg":"但條脷有刺"},{"pid":"3ada9e366aa26ca7feac77c01a3406f715d46f8c","tid":1146699,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-09T15:35:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ae6e6bf07c3671d8a096ddd6078